{"tid":1975560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大火11天！男童用打火機煙燻松鼠洞 燒掉四川大片山頭","createTime":"2020-04-16T15:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T21:56:46.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"75f1e1d3988c306a4f27d2256a0b8ec456269a5e","tid":1975560,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"大火11天！男童用打火機煙燻松鼠洞 燒掉四川大片山頭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3131352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3131352&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10C8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=d8071117\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3131352&h=32a173f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3131352</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國四川省涼山州木里縣3月28日晚間起發生森林大火，火勢延燒11天，至本月8日才被撲滅，中方目前調查出，整起山林大火是因1名11歲男孩用打火機所致。<br />\n<br />\n根據《京報網》報導，涼山木里縣3月28日晚間7時發生森林大火，起火點從喬瓦鎮鋤頭灣村、項腳鄉項腳村交界處開始蔓延，當地有大量雲南松、雜灌等植物，加上風勢影響火勢迅速延燒，當局派出3000人搶救，仍然無法有效控制火勢，大火延燒11天，至本月8日才被撲滅。<br />\n<br />\n中國國家森林草原防滅火指揮部辦公室本月約談四川省、涼山州人民政府負責人，當地在3月發生42起森林草原火災，比起去年同期多出163%，發生在涼山州西昌市的森林大火，甚至造成19名地方撲火人員犧牲、3名地方撲火隊員重傷，多幢民房燒毀，損失慘重。<br />\n<br />\n四川省木里藏族自治縣人民政府辦公室官方微博今（12）日指出，當地森林火災案，經查後發現是因1名11歲的男孩，在3月28日下午2點在自家後山上點燃木羅松，想煙燻松鼠洞卻引發火災，目前此案正在進一步偵查中。"},{"pid":"96e3486085a357406d8ed43c86a11ab064b8d955","tid":1975560,"uid":199957,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jsB4nda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjsB4nda.jpg&h=9a61a49f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b04bddb1522a79a2b8b8694f6688deee52f83ad","tid":1975560,"uid":60773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"牠只是個孩子呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c5e92b1a25c9e13cefcf08786b39dbab1cfab4","tid":1975560,"uid":161274,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"回力鏢又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b76cde6603b053e273b6a386444b5a5e49e323","tid":1975560,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"個細路咁細個已經識燒山反共，有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb7b0a93d94eb8235967bb8525cd0cdf4c4f630","tid":1975560,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31b76cde6603b053e273b6a386444b5a5e49e323","tid":1975560,"uid":254450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"個細路咁細個已經識燒山反共，有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:34:41.000Z","msg":"反共原來咁簡單。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d842f515f70b3cfa2276d9c8694e4250cb18b79","tid":1975560,"uid":58852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"燒山好嘢多謝燒山"},{"pid":"bea017ad8517b60842c50b9b57aa50a21ac950c8","tid":1975560,"uid":7940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:51:11.000Z","msg":"諗住燒人全家，點知燒埋自己全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1615be1e3e5dc5dfac62c7ccef62615ff5360611","tid":1975560,"uid":13343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:12:12.000Z","msg":"又話救山火好勁？ <br />\n之前又話咩如果澳洲山火喺佢地到發生用一個禮拜一定救得熄？<br />\n呢場火唔會大過澳洲山火掛？"},{"pid":"921c3e939b39130a716eb95b3a356145ccb4b539","tid":1975560,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"燒生好野"},{"pid":"f6afe0ae948605b7801b49b4e75e3747cac4d367","tid":19755